{
  "stem": "7683.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, to be honest, I didn't have too much to do with it when I lived in Lodz, which is a bigger city, I was-- I didn't-- I didn't have friends with really-- much friends, many friends, would have been not Jews.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember in Lodz there was an [INAUDIBLE] in the city, but I wouldn't go as a Jew there because I knew it is a not-Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was really afraid to go there, whether it was a reason, but just that we felt that way.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was a lot of anti-Semitism, but I personally didn't experience it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was, in the time when Hitler came, I was a soldier in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was already one and a half year in the army, so I don't know what had truly changed, but the whole Poland is gone-- was gone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They occupied in three weeks, and I was-- three weeks I was in the war, in the war as a Polish soldier.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah, probably 19. 19, something like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, drafted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, drafted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody had to be one and a half year in the army, and that was my time I went there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I am supposed to be freed on November the 15th, was my time expired, but the war broke out September the 1st, so it caught me in the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three weeks later, I was-- became a prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took me to Germany with all prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in Germany till March, half March, when they decided to send all Jewish prisoners of war back to Poland because they had already the plans for the Jews, so they didn't keep them as prisoners of war in Poland-- in Germany.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They sent them back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
